{"title":"各族人民齐歌唱","authors":["刘保厚","龙云中","何要平","杨光芬"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":11,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族人民齐歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条银河从天降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢水奔流映红光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老君毁掉八卦炉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投拜农民学炼钢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（刘保厚）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年庄稼真不弱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜煞八十老公婆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公公说是竹笋子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"婆婆说是森林坡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（彝族龙云中唱）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群群大山围小山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要把群山搬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬开小山修公路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬开大山成良田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（苗族何要平）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳出来遍地红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花开出一大蓬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席好比红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族人民好比花一蓬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人歌唱毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花向阳朵朵红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（布依族杨光芬）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}